% Parallel branches ReceiveTask_1 and ReceiveTask_2 under ParallelGateway_1 should be reachable in both observable orders.
% Both observable branch orders should be reachable.
<true* . (exists oid: OrderId. c_send_manifest(oid)) . true* . (exists oid: OrderId. c_send_eir(oid))>true &&
<true* . (exists oid: OrderId. c_send_eir(oid)) . true* . (exists oid: OrderId. c_send_manifest(oid))>true